{"tid":2494950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警致函抗議學童玩槍報道 《蘋果》：基於事實報道","createTime":"2021-04-19T01:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T02:12:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4c892a00b565fd562742d2c17fee8ad8588ceea2","tid":2494950,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:40:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/MMOHPA4WDFFVBCTEIHWBWUX3ME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2FMMOHPA4WDFFVBCTEIHWBWUX3ME%2F&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVph9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=c8ce1503\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2FMMOHPA4WDFFVBCTEIHWBWUX3ME%2F&h=14968825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/MMOHPA4WDFFVBCTEIHWBWUX3ME/</a><br />\n<br />\n警致函抗議學童玩槍報道<br />\n《蘋果》：基於事實報道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eYHJU7YzE_jmXRoAiO-HFhei5Oo=/510x707/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2NR5R7FYCZFX7IFNCG2FSOACFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeYHJU7YzE_jmXRoAiO-HFhei5Oo%3D%2F510x707%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2NR5R7FYCZFX7IFNCG2FSOACFI.jpg&h=8aabfc0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方上周五致函本報指有關學童在警察學院玩槍的報道分化。<br />\n<br />\n手機用戶請按此放大圖表<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警務處長鄧炳強連日不點名批評《蘋果日報》，指本報上周五（16日）頭版有關學童在警察學院玩槍的報道分化和煽動仇恨。警方在報道刊登當日致函《蘋果》，稱有關頭版報道刊登了開放日活動一幀小童玩耍的照片，說明卻加以扭曲，指有網民將照片與前年「8.31」太子站發生的事件連繫在一起，質疑警隊「向下一代教育了甚麼？」警方認為手法不道德，故需澄清，並作強烈抗議。《蘋果日報》昨日回應，強調是基於事實報道，《蘋果》編輯自主，並根據《基本法》享有新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n當日《蘋果日報》報道，警察學院因應國家安全教育日舉行開放日，報道選取了路透社的相片，相中有學童在模擬地鐵車廂內拿起玩具衝鋒槍，指向同伴的腦袋。報道引述有網民指，驚訝場面恍如重演香港警察在8.31太子站舉槍指向乘客的一幕。有關相片亦引發網民熱議，不少網民、KOL、甚至台灣媒體（聯合新聞網）都聯想8.31場面。"},{"pid":"992499099a8d1a2b893df01c50092a17524b8b67","tid":2494950,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b622614b0ccc93a716962df2ecad5bf46066093","tid":2494950,"uid":26672,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:46:42.000Z","msg":"你d相就係當時影嘅，831都係活生生發生左，將兩樣事實拼合左會變失實，真係得垃圾黑警先會諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我第一眼都已經覺得似831啦，根本好多正常人都會咁諗"},{"pid":"1c37c95baf2d013acd72d88f6a8daad44e51e12e","tid":2494950,"uid":19527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:49:34.000Z","msg":"831咁英勇嘅事，蘋果讚下你地都唔得？"},{"pid":"dc5de37a0cafd80d0267020639626d166ec39cfc","tid":2494950,"uid":83523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:00:17.000Z","msg":"跟本就無私顯見私<br />\n<br />\n你地黑警覺得831無問題，班細路模仿當日情景都無問題架。<br />\n<br />\n除非連你地都覺得831有好大問題啦"},{"pid":"0d4f7b631d85b90ddf4f53ad39102eae1cb298d8","tid":2494950,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:00:18.000Z","msg":"幾時投訴埋連登？<br />\n<br />\n明明連登仔講得仲多<br />\n<br />\n死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80a13f50ddb695fac98b4ae1d0ef5bffcf557a3","tid":2494950,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVANWj2Fnt4D971P76HK9aftGUuAGmHis3NyCbp5AUaC6?filename=XeADPyK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXeADPyK.gif&h=675635f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f8d17d9f864ac97d7780ec227cb2ccea27616f5","tid":2494950,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:07:10.000Z","msg":"唔係想洗白整個黨鐵車箱做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知比班靚仔玩爛左就輸打贏要"},{"pid":"bc3e82805d6692dd25aae0021478b